{"type": "article", "id": 27098, "title": "果酱和茶叶包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-20T06:55:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130804FuG2ZMirHDaYNOSt.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>当产地本身就有好的素材可以利用，想要让包装第一时间抓住人们的眼球并不是件难事：<a href=\"http://pseftogas.com/\">noon design+branding</a> 为 Kalifyton 的茶叶和果酱做的这套设计就是在希腊渊源这一点上下足了功夫。以古希腊诗歌作为灵感，在沙棘果产品的包装上使用了马的图案（据传受伤的马因为吃了这种果实而痊愈），在以其他水果制成的产品包装上则印上了衔着果实站在枝头的小鸟，表现出与自然和谐共处的生活方式。在向传统致敬的同时，又体现了当代的设计感，让人眼前一亮。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021308025mXjLONCZcy3MDWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130802r3ynp8PENJVuW4ic.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130803HrQY4txTd0qV2afE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130803F82RXGDgCnTSpOUr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}